" Commands and keybindings
"
" - call Git/tig commands with the current file
" - call diff --cached to show whats stages (in index)

command! Gitblame :execute "silent !tig blame -- %" | execute "redraw!"
command! Gitindexdiff :execute "!git diff --cached"

:nmap <F10>gb :Gitblame<CR>
:nmap <F10>gi :Gitindexdiff<CR>
